    "Fashion compatibility involves calculating the overall harmony of an outfit.",
    "Obviously, it is insufficient to treat clothing as a sequence and to focus only on the relationships between items, as this approach will overlook the overall harmony between item sets.",
    "Fashion compatibility learning has many important application scenarios in both the physical world and the Metaverse.",
    "It can help designers and consumers to select clothing, and can provide quantitative matching assistance for high-level fashion technologies.",
    "In the Metaverse, individuals have unlimited possibilities for creation, interaction, and exploration."
